# Note: we intentionally do NOT ignore *.xcodeproj at repo level — the
# example app under Examples/ ships its xcodeproj so users can clone
# and run it without recreating the project. SPM-generated transient
# xcodeproj files live in DerivedData (already excluded) and never
# appear in the working tree.

